": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "529": {"data": {"tag_id": 529, "tag_name": "说唱", "cover": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/79f1ff3b7bb5c422c6f9dc8f7e1bb36b4de2b201.jpg", "head_cover": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/c427fec8e9501db6294a2a286e4bbe2d0cfb9646.jpg", "content": "说唱音乐是一种跟着伴奏、带着韵律吟诵的音乐风格，诞生于美国1970年代，并于1980年代成为大众流行文化之一。", "short_content": "说唱音乐相关。", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "1817": {"data": {"tag_id": 1817, "tag_name": "MV", "cover": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/bf0497d27bcded85a9384fc5c814e966fddfffdf.jpg", "head_cover": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/2bd98de8e6fe0af41d9ca264a8e10b087e365ef6.jpg", "content": "MV,即音乐短片（Music Video），是指与音乐搭配的短片，主要是为了作为宣传音乐唱片而制作。", "short_content": "音乐录影带，看见好音乐。", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "295610": {"data": {"tag_id": 295610, "tag_name": "老番茄", "cover": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/tag/571bee9c51c3b85ea4d389a144a36f2cd01e0382.jpg", "head_cover": "", "content": "老番茄，游戏区知名UP主，2013年底依靠脑洞剧情向搞笑解说视频《你可XX如此丧病的口袋妖怪解说？》系列红遍某同性交友网站。早期节目还有《番茄扯蛋》系列、实况小游戏等。经过高三一年闭关，过气网红（× 老番茄高调复出，推出第二部口袋妖怪系列视频《赵赵的奇幻之旅！》，同时正在不定期更新《极限推理！恒水中学连环虐杀！》实况解说。和@Chimera君是一被子好基友。 老番茄新浪微博@_老番茄_：http://www.weibo.com/u/3708072513?from=feed&loc=nickname 百度贴吧@老番茄吧：http://tieba.baidu.com/f?ie=utf-8&kw=%E8%80%81%E7%95%AA%E8%8C%84", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1},